snippet: A student who said she was sexually assaulted by three members of the University of Oregon men's basketball team sent an open letter to the school newspaper in which she asserts the athletic department prioritizes winning over student safety....

headline.print_headline: Oregon Basketball Rape Accuser: 'I Am Angry'
headline.main: Oregon Basketball Rape Accuser: 'I Am Angry'

lead_paragraph: A student who said she was sexually assaulted by three members of the University of Oregon men's basketball team sent an open letter to the school newspaper in which she asserts the athletic department prioritizes winning over student safety.
